User Story 1: User Registration
As a user, I want to be able to register on the platform to have access to a personal account and its features.

Given that I am an unregistered user and I am on the homepage
When I click the "Register" link at the top of the page
Then I fill in my personal data (name, email, password)
And click the "Register" button
Then system shows me the message about account confirmation
When I confirm my email
Then the website opens for me on the main page with my account
User Story 2: Adding a Product to the Cart
As a buyer, I want to be able to add products to the cart to conveniently build an order before purchase.

Given that I am an authorized user
When I'm on the main product page and see the list of available products
Then I click the "Add to Cart" button next to the desired product.
When I finish the selection, I will go to the "Cart" page.
Then I finally decide what I need (remove unnecessary products from the Cart) and order the product.
User Story 3: Viewing Order History
As a registered user, I want to be able to view the history of my orders to track their status and details.

Given I am an authorized user and have made purchases before,
When I'm on my account page,
Then I click the "Order History" button,
When a list of all orders made by me appears.
Then I can click on a specific order,
Then I will see detailed information about the order.
